lead_paragraph: Chris Carter hit two long home runs and drove in three, Junior Guerra won his first career major league start, and the Milwaukee Brewers rallied from an early four-run deficit to beat the Los Angeles Angels 5-4 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Chris Carter Goes Deep Twice, Brewers Beat Angels 5-4
